name: I Wrote You a Love Letter, Necklace
description:
This charming necklace hangs from a delicate gold plated chain. The focal point of the piece is a verdigris finish envelope which opens to reveal a brass postcard that says "I Love You" . This necklace measures approximately 20 inches and closes with a gold plated clasp.

*PLEASE NOTE: The verdigris finish will differ from piece to piece and may be much darker than pictured*

Want these for NON-PIERCED EARS? Send me a message and I will create them for you!

All pieces are packaged with care in a small organza bag or kraft box.

name: Love is All You Need, Earrings
description:
Two adorable vintage style pink flower cabochons sit atop surgical steel post earwires. The flowers measure a quarter of an inch in diameter and the ear posts are hypoallergenic.

All pieces are packaged with care in a small organza bag or kraft box.

name: She Doth Not Wait for June, Earrings
description:
These lovely earrings hang from antique copper earwires. From each earwire dangles a delicate antique bronze filigree filigree pendant that I hand finished in a pale shade of lilac. The pendants are accented by maroon vintage cabochons and measure about 2 inches diameter. The earrings hang 3 inches from the ear.

Want these for NON-PIERCED EARS? Send me a message and I will create them for you!

All pieces are packaged with care in a small organza bag or kraft box.

name: Interlude, Ring
description:
A lovely vintage style pale peach pink rose cabochon sits on an antique silver adjustable filigree ring. The blossom measures about 1/2 of an inch in diameter. The band can easily be adjusted to fit any size finger.

All pieces are packaged with care in a small organza bag or kraft box.

name: Fairytale, Pair of Bobby Pins
description:
This set is made up of two charming silver bobby pins. The first bobby pin is accented by a vintage creamy white rose cabochon and the second is accented by a vintage turquoise leaf cabochon. These bobby pins measure approximately 2 inches in length.

All pieces are packaged with care in a small organza bag or kraft box.
